Sami ste rekli da nema cipele.

129
00:14:53,280 --> 00:14:55,080
Proverimo drugu stranu.

130
00:14:59,280 --> 00:15:05,120
Šta je ono?
-Stari svetionik, već je pretražen.

131
00:15:08,360 --> 00:15:12,360
